		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You call upon the power of darkness to isolate your target as they lose both sight and hearing.</em></p><p><strong>[[/save constitution]]{Constitution Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target is &amp;reference[blinded] and &amp;reference[deafened]. If you want, you can cause only one of the conditions to take effect. Target rolls again at end of their turns, ending effect on success.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Upcasting:</strong> Target one additional creature for each spell level above 2nd.</p>",
